snippet.title: BH KickstarterVideo
snippet.description:
Our highly acclaimed Adventure Game, Brain Hotel, is getting a remake! We can use all the support we can get to bring this game to life, so please consider checking out the Kickstarter page to reserve your copy and see what cool rewards you can get!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pinheadgames/brain-hotel-remodeled
